content: in the Oct PERIOD   edition of The Daily Illini the article Hiltzik makes quarterfinal fails to qualify for ITA nationals was published with a fabricated quote attributed to Illinois mens tennis player Jared Hiltzik PERIOD The quote has since been removed from the online version of the article PERIOD The Daily Illini regrets the error PERIOD
title: Correction for "Hiltzik makes quarterfinal, fails to qualify for ITA nationals" published on Oct. 7, 2013 - The Daily Illini
name: University of Illinois Urbana Champaign
